{"tid":2163072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果決定參與臨立會嘅泛民議員承諾入到去會開打","createTime":"2020-08-18T12:38:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T14:04:34.000Z","uid":275907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eb78286db8ae9b0c23eb84f37a80fa5e88075f02","tid":2163072,"uid":275907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"最起碼好似台灣議員衝擊嘅程度 <br />\n<br />\n咁就各自爬山啦（但我內心依然反對參與）<br />\n<br />\n但如果好似以前咁舉下牌叫下嘅話就收皮啦.......<br />\n<br />\n唔好話老做唔到 人哋個啲都係阿叔阿嬸 <br />\n<br />\n係而家依個環境阻惡法通過（泛民參與臨立會論點）除咗肢體衝突我諗唔到其他<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實之前話阻惡法個啲 我諗好多人都感受唔到你哋嘅決心 所以先對議會戰線死心<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲嚟講 得把口 <br />\n<br />\n睇吓台灣議員就知咩叫決心......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_uuDHn5LLUw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_uuDHn5LLUw&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5sF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=4b68f634\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_uuDHn5LLUw</a>"},{"pid":"bf3f56298a6a356ef02bc4fc9468200d4c22ccee","tid":2163072,"uid":47810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:43:45.000Z","msg":"泛民先唔會打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa69a0a2283c88463048a8b889c0506768087492","tid":2163072,"uid":275907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf3f56298a6a356ef02bc4fc9468200d4c22ccee","tid":2163072,"uid":47810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:43:45.000Z","msg":"泛民先唔會打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:48:31.000Z","msg":"睇死頂盡都係好似big暈咁扮衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ca13cfa01869e0e35922d69af9d80e7ef54832","tid":2163072,"uid":47810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa69a0a2283c88463048a8b889c0506768087492","tid":2163072,"uid":275907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf3f56298a6a356ef02bc4fc9468200d4c22ccee